    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Exceptional mint-condition example that presents about as well as you could hope for, with outstanding paint, trim, interior, and overall finish. It appears complete, highly cared for, and ready for a buyer who wants a top-tier car rather than just a usable driver. Expect a very sharp, highly original-looking and/or properly restored presentation with minimal visible wear and the kind of detail that stands out immediately in person.",
