    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Exceptionally clean mint-condition car that shows extremely well inside and out. The paint, interior, trim, and overall presentation reflect a very well-kept example with only the kind of minimal signs of use you\u2019d expect from a properly cared-for car. It starts, runs, and drives like a standout vehicle, and a buyer should expect a car that feels clean, sorted, and ready to enjoy right away.",
      "price": 46900.0,
