    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers straightforward transportation at an accessible price. Best suited for a buyer who values affordability and practicality, it presents an opportunity to own a dependable daily driver or project candidate without a major investment. A sensible choice for someone seeking honest value and low-cost entry into vehicle ownership.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable project, parts car, or basic runaround with some potential? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest used car with plenty of life left for the right buyer. A great option for someone handy, a first project, or anyone who wants something inexpensive without spending a fortune. Priced to reflect its condition, and a nice chance to grab a car with value and possibilities.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver/project with a strong-running powertrain and good bones. It shows cosmetic wear and needs attention in places, but the engine pulls well, the transmission engages as it should, and it has the kind of straightforward mechanical layout that makes it appealing for someone who wants dependable basic transportation or a weekend fixer. A great chance to get into an affordable car with usable road manners and plenty of upside for the next owner.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way to get on the road. Cosmetic wear and age show, but it still does the job. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough with undeniable personality, this car has the kind of well-traveled character that turns errands into stories and projects into possibilities. It\u2019s an affordable way to get behind the wheel of something with presence, charm, and plenty of potential for the right buyer\u2014whether you need a budget-friendly runabout, a hands-on project, or a dependable companion for the next chapter. Priced to reflect its condition while still offering a lot of heart, this is the kind of opportunity that rewards vision.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle is a practical choice for a buyer seeking dependable basic transportation at an accessible price point. It offers strong value for the money, a straightforward ownership proposition, and an opportunity for the next owner to make it their own. If you're looking for an inexpensive vehicle with honest appeal and everyday usefulness, this one is well worth a look.",
      "price": 4950.0,
